### Create Kafka source connector
POST {{kurrent.url}}/connectors/{{kafka.source.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "settings": {
    "instanceTypeName": "kafka-source",
    "topic": "{{kafka.topic}}",
    "partition": "0",
    "offset": "29",
    "schemaRegistry:url": "{{kafka.schemaRegistry.url}}",
    "consumer:bootstrapServers": "{{kafka.consumer.bootstrapServers}}",
    "consumer:autoOffsetReset": "latest",
    "consumer:enableAutoCommit": "true",
    "consumer:autoCommitIntervalMs": "5000",
    "consumer:allowAutoCreateTopics": "true",
    "consumer:enableAutoOffsetStore": "false"
  }
}

### Start Kafka source connector
POST {{kurrent.url}}/connectors/{{kafka.source.id}}/start

### Produce Order Placed Event to Kafka topic (Schema Registry)
POST {{kafka.restProxy}}/topics/{{kafka.topic}}
Content-Type: application/vnd.kafka.jsonschema.v2+json
Accept: application/vnd.kafka.v2+json

