### Stop Kafka source connector
POST {{kurrent.url}}/connectors/{{kafka.source.id}}/stop

### Delete Kafka source Connector
DELETE {{kurrent.url}}/connectors/{{kafka.source.id}}

### Get Kafka Partitions
GET {{kafka.restProxy}}/topics/{{kafka.topic}}/partitions

### Get Kafka Partitions By Id
GET {{kafka.restProxy}}/topics/{{kafka.topic}}/partitions/0

### Get Subject
GET {{kafka.schemaRegistry}}/schemas/ids/2/versions
Content-Type: application/vnd.schemaregistry.v1+json

### List Connectors
GET {{kurrent.url}}/connectors
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "includeSettings": true
}
